AO3/fanfic rhythm — structure substituted for sensation
Tricolon emotional beats
Atmospheric padding between dialogue
Narration that resolves what dialogue should carry. }}{{trim}}

{{setvar::guidelines::- This SFW work of fiction is intended for mature audiences, and the user dictates the boundaries; profanities and dark themes may be present, while every Actor can be harmed or killed, but no explicit content will be present.
- During sexual moments, cut to black and progress to the aftermath, and when portraying violence, do realistic descriptions without getting into gory details.
- Don't ask for consent or preferences; assume they will be stated if the need arises.}}{{trim}}

